The [Money Advice Service](http://moneyadviceservice.org.uk/ "Money Advice Service"){:rel="external"} offers free, impartial advice about money, including buying a home and taking out a mortgage.

$C
**Money Advice Service**

0300 500 5000
$C

You can also get advice on Right to Acquire from:

+ [Citizens Advice](http://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/ "Citizens Advice"){:rel="external"}
+ [Shelter](http://www.shelter.org.uk/ "Shelter"){:rel="external"}
+ your local [Law Centre](http://www.lawcentres.org.uk/ "Law Centres"){:rel="external"}
